fields.name: Shania Twain
fields.bio: Eilleen Regina Shania Twain OC is a Canadian singer-songwriter and actress. She is one of the best-selling music artists of all time and the best-selling female artist in country music history. Her success garnered her several titles including the Queen of Country Pop

fields.name: Taylor Swift
fields.bio: Taylor Alison Swift is an American singer-songwriter. Recognized for her genre-spanning discography, songwriting, and artistic reinventions, Swift is a prominent cultural figure who has been cited as an influence on a generation of music artists

fields.name: Chris Stapleton
fields.bio: Christopher Alvin Stapleton is an American singer-songwriter, guitarist, and record producer. He was born in Lexington, Kentucky, and grew up in Staffordsville, Kentucky.
